                <h1>Understanding Walmart's Hiring Process: A Step-by-Step Guide</h1>
                <p>Walmart's hiring process typically involves several steps. Candidates submit applications online, followed by an assessment test to gauge skills. If successful, interviews may be conducted, often with a focus on customer service values and team collaboration. Finally, background checks are standard before an offer is made, ensuring a good fit for the company.</p>
